Okay, here's the deal. Replace data folder from here with the one from your Lugaru install.
Make sure you have SDL, libjpeg, libGL, libOGG and libVorbis installed.
Navigate to this folder in a terminal and type make, (if you're on Ubuntu, get the
build-essential package from Synaptic Package Manager.)
